Description 1: Connect Danswer to your organization's knowledge sources. We'll automatically sync your data into Danswer, so you can find exactly what you're looking for in one place.
Import Knowledge - Description: Connect to pieces of knowledge that live outside your apps. Upload files, scrape websites, or connect to your organization's Google Site.
Setup Auto-Syncing from Apps - Descripti: Setup auto-syncing from your organization's most used apps and services. Unless otherwise specified during the connector setup, we will pull in the latest updates from the source every 10 minutes.
